-- Apple CFO expects flat gross margin in 3rd-quarter
-- 
-- Wed Apr 23, 2008 7:51pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/04/23/us-apple-margin-idUSN2343217820080423

 

 SAN FRANCISCO  (Reuters) - Apple Inc ( AAPL.O ) expects gross margins in its current, third fiscal quarter to be flat with the second quarter's 32.9 percent, Chief Financial Officer Peter Oppenheimer said on Wednesday. 

 "We are guiding for gross margin to be flat in (the) June (quarter)," Oppenheimer said in an interview. (Reporting by  Scott Hillis )